{"tid":293002,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"又同女朋友散左","createTime":"2017-06-21T21:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T23:41:31.000Z","uid":11906,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"234f1b90ac38805b1a68e4cb276ab20dbff270b7","tid":293002,"uid":11906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T21:58:46.000Z","msg":"今次係同佢第八次拍拖<br />\n頭七次係中一中二個陣<br />\n大家都係初戀<br />\n五年後係我地係個旅行一齊返<br />\n我宜家感覺返左黎<br />\n我好愛佢<br />\n好想同佢行落去<br />\n但佢同我講我哋兩個世界嘅人<br />\n我唔玩唔飲酒 佢就成日去玩<br />\n好辛苦 好想麻醉自己"},{"pid":"2758b6daa3eae82de42b15c4fa6da95ebcb895e6","tid":293002,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T22:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 情聖"},{"pid":"354150a2c948cc07f7870ebb573e779cff9a6e06","tid":293002,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T22:11:58.000Z","msg":"5p全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1581a217d11467f767331c5a14c82a020aeb6a","tid":293002,"uid":2719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T22:13:32.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 屍朗寶寶 )"},{"pid":"f27af2b442c7046a01b201537cc937385e54e179","tid":293002,"uid":99212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T22:13:50.000Z","msg":"中一中二兩年離離合合拍七次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e8714389e0b18d31171e22801a12bf695b1722","tid":293002,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T22:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分手咁多次"},{"pid":"350